v3.1.2 Release Notes

- Framework-updater skill now includes canonical upstream URL
- Consumer projects can run: git remote add upstream https://github.com/kelleysd-apps/sdd-agentic-framework.git
- Enables /update-framework command to properly sync framework updates

Setup for consumer projects:
  git remote add upstream https://github.com/kelleysd-apps/sdd-agentic-framework.git
  git fetch upstream
